HAS-A Mapping And IS-A Mapping :
==================================

- person class has a relation with address class. (HAS-A b/w two class)
- IS-A -> Inheritance

**-> On object we have has-A relationship but at table level we don't have this kind of any relationship.
     This a mismatch.
     This is mismatch is called Granularity Mismatch.


==> How can we do that ?
    @Embedded keyword











